descript.abstract: [Metadata] Locations of Preschools, Early Education and Early Childcare Centers in the State of Hawaii as of December 2021. Source: Executive Office of Early Learning (EOEL); People Attentive To Children (PATCH), December 2021. For more information, please see metadata at https://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/op/gis/data/preschools.pdf or contact Hawaii Statewide GIS Program, Office of Planning and Sustainable Development, State of Hawaii; PO Box 2359, Honolulu, Hi. 96804; (808) 587-2846; email: gis@hawaii.gov; Website: https://planning.hawaii.gov/gis.
